## ‚ö†Ô∏è ASSETS WE AVOIDED (And Why)

### **‚ùå Natural Gas (NGAS) - 55% Predictable**
- TOO volatile (5-10% daily swings)
- Weather-driven (fundamentals > technicals)
- Requires 5%+ stop-loss (vs. 2.36%)
- Seasonal adjustments needed
- **Verdict:** Not worth the risk

### **‚ùå Tesla (TSLA) - 75% Predictable**
- Gap risk (16+ hours market closed)
- Earnings shocks (4√ó/year invalidate patterns)
- Elon tweet risk (5-10% overnight gaps)
- Single company risk
- **Verdict:** Use S&P 500 (SPY) instead for stock exposure

### **‚ùå Bitcoin/Ethereum - 45-50% Predictable**
- Extreme manipulation (whales)
- 24/7 market (gap risk everywhere)
- Regulatory shocks
- Social media driven
- **Verdict:** Only for experienced crypto traders

### **‚ùå USD/JPY, AUD/USD - 70-73% Predictable**
- Lower predictability than top 4
- Similar roles covered by EUR/USD, GBP/USD
- Would increase API calls (less efficient)
- **Verdict:** Keep portfolio lean and focused

